      <div xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258">
        <head xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Hd1e99" type="question-title">De taciturnitate</head>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e102">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e112" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e104">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e112">Discrete vicissitudinum pensanda sunt tempora:
              ne aut, cum restringi debet lingua, per verba se inutiliter solvat; aut, cum loqui
              utiliter potest, semetipsam pigra restringat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e117">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e127" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e119">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e127">Si ab increpatione idcirco reticemus, quia
              contra nos insurgere derisoris odia formidamus; non jam lucra Dei quaerimus, sed
              nostra.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e132">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e142" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e134">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e142">Quoties auditores nostri nostra volunt quasi
              laudando cognoscere, non autem sua perversa mutare, omnia taceamus: ne si
              ostentationis studio verbum Dei loquimur, et illorum culpa, quae erat, esse non
              desinat, et nostra, quae non erat, fiat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e147">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e157" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e149">Gregorius, in <title>Homiliis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e157">Imitatione Dei, gloriosius est tacendo injuriam
              fugere, quam respondendo superare.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e163">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e173" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e165">Gregorius, <title>super Ezechielem</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e173">Quasi quoddam nutrimentum verbi est censura
              silentii; et recte per excrescentem quoque gratiam sermonem accipit, qui ordinate
              antea per humilitatem tacet.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e178">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e188" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e180">Gregorius, <title>super Ezechielem</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e188">Sicut mali ideo Deum exasperant, quia loquuntur
              et faciunt mala; ita nonnunquam boni exasperant, quia reticent bona.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e193">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e203" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e195">Gregorius, in <title>Pastorali</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e203">Qui proximi mala respiciunt, et tamen silentio
              linguam premunt, quasi conspectis vulneribus, usum medicaminis subtrahunt, et eo
              mortis auctores fiunt, quo minus, quem poterant, curare volunt.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e208">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e218" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e210">Hieronymus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e218">Nunquam de mulierum formis disputes; nec quid in
              cujusquam domo agitur, alia domus per te noverit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e223">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e233" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e225">Augustinus, <title>de Mendacio</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e233">Licet vel dissertori, ac disputatori, ac
              praedicatori rerum aeternarum, vel narratori atque pronuntiatori rerum temporalium, ad
              aedificandam religionem atque pietatem pertinentium, occultare in tempore quidquid
              occultandum videtur; mentiri autem, nunquam.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e238">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e248" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e240">Augustinus, <title>de Baptismo parvulorum</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e248">Ubi de re obscurissima disputatur, non
              adjuvantibus divinarum Scripturarum certis clarisque documentis, cohibere se debet
              humana praesumptio, nihil faciens in partem alteram declinando.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e254">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e264" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e256">Isidorus, in <title>Synonymis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e264">Tempore congruo loquere; tempore congruo tace;
              non loquaris, nisi interrogatus fueris; non dicas, priusquam audias.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e269">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e279" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e271">Isidorus, in <title>Synonymis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e279">Ab otioso sermone compesce linguam; cave fabulas
              ineptas; aniles fabulas non requiras; inania verba non garrias.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e284">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e294" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e286">Isidorus, in <title>Synonymis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e294">Vis virtutes tuas augere? prodere noli.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e299">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e309" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e301">Isidorus, in <title>Synonymis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e309">Fuge videri quod esse meruisti: quod
              manifestando potes amittere, tacendo custodi.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e314">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e324" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e316">Ambrosius, <title>super Lucam</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e324">Rarior tacendi virtus, quam loquendi.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e329">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e339" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e331">Ambrosius, <title>de Officiis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e339">Quamplures vidi loquendo in peccatum incidisse;
              vix quemquam tacendo: ideoque tacere nosse, quam loqui, difficilius est.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e345">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e355" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e347">Ambrosius, <title>de Officiis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e355">Quando nobis aliquis conviciatur, lacessit, ad
              violentiam provocat, ad jurgium vocat; tunc silentium exerceamus, tunc muti fieri non
              erubescamus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e360">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e370" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e362">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e370">Utilis semper custodia oris, quae tamen
              affabilitatis gratiam non excludat. Ergo ubique fraenanda lingua praeceps, maxime
              autem in convivio.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-d1e375">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e385" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Rd1e377">Glossa in <title>Leviticum</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e37258-Qd1e385">Quod gula peccavit, jejunium corrigat: quod
              garrulitas admisit, silentium deleat; et similiter contrariis curentur
              contraria.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
      </div>
